title: Ecosystem Illustration
description: An illustration depicting a vibrant ecosystem. On the left, a small lizard is resting on a rock surrounded by colorful flowers. In the center, a flowering plant stands tall, showcasing pink blooms. To the right, a large tree with a thick trunk and lush green foliage is depicted, with its roots visible underground. Above, several birds are flying in the sky, contributing to the lively atmosphere of the scene.

title: Fresh Cherries on a Branch
description: A cluster of four shiny, red cherries attached to a branch with two green leaves.
